{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"184f560b92","title":"毛泽东对李维汉关于资本主义工商业改造问题发言稿的批语和修改时加写的部分内容","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"41058d9a73","index":0,"year":1955,"month":11,"day":22,"articleId":"184f560b92"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0ad79614cf","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对李维汉关于资本主义工商业改造问题发言稿的批语和修改时加写的部分内容","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92"},{"id":"d69f4f519c","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92"},{"id":"374b992e4d","type":"appellation","text":"即送李维汉同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92"},{"id":"40f1ccb1de","type":"paragraph","text":"此件可用。有一些修改，请你考虑是否可用。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92"},{"id":"2e0464aa61","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十一月廿二日下午十时半根据手稿刊印。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92"},{"id":"25a21b2c7c","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92"},{"id":"76e6d51bb5","type":"paragraph","text":"在公私合营形式上的企业改造，首先是资本主义所有制在很大程度上的社会主义改造，这种企业已经是“四分之三的社会主义”企业了。既已合营了之后，即转入经营管理。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92"},{"id":"8f334dce5c","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92"},{"id":"6f690d06a2","type":"paragraph","text":"除了大约占百分之几的具有严重情况的反革命分子及其他坏分子以外，其余的应当肯定是可以用又鼓励又批评的教育方法加以改造的。批评就是对于他们的主要的斗争方式。当然还要加对违法者给予罚款等等一项斗争方式。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92"}],"page":{"id":"37483790a3","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"184f560b92","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}